headline: Zacks Industry Outlook Highlights Skyworks and Qorvo

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell SWKS and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: What a brutal six months it’s been for Skyworks Solutions. The stock has dropped 22.1% and now trades at $68.92, rattling many shareholders. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
